    work — as long as your organization has at most FIVE (5) total users of
    Workspacer.

  - Once an organization has six (6) or more total users, that organization
    needs a commercial license. Reach out at djtouchette1993@gmail.com.

  - You may not offer Workspacer to third parties as a hosted or managed
    service, or resell it, without a commercial license.

  - Four years after each version is published, that version automatically
    becomes available under the MIT License (see "Change Date" and
    "Change License" below).

